{"type":null,"faqId":10901,"title":"荣耀3C （H30-T10&H30-U10）  静态IP进行使用WLAN上网","answer":"<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">无线和网络</span></b><span> &gt; <b>WLAN</b></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，点击要连接的热点，在弹出的对话框中，勾选<b>高级选项</b>，在</span><span>IP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置里选择<b>静态</b>，依次填写</span><b><span>IP</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">地址</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">（通常设置为</span><span>192.168.1.***</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）、<b>网关</b>（通常都是</span><span>192.168.1.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）、<b>子网掩码或网络掩码</b>（</span><span>255.255.255.0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）和<b>域名</b>（</span><span>dns</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">地址）就可以了。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31977\" /><br />\n</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> \n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">使用</span><span>WLAN</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">入网络最大的问题就是不能实现免等待连接网络，移动设备连接上路由器之后会获取一个动态的</span><span>IP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">地址，比较费时。使用静态</span><span>IP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的进行</span><span>WLAN</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">上网，就可以实现急速上网。</span> \n\t</p>\n<br />\n</span> \n\t<p>\n\t\t<br />\n\t</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1661","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1397785833000,"seriesProductName":"H30-T10,H30-U10","visitedTimes":334,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀3C （H30-T10&H30-U10）","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}